'''Ganth''' was the personal [[Security droid/Legends|security droid]] of [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Tovir Daglear]]. The [[Droid/Legends|droid]] accompanied Daglear to the annual [[Spira Regatta Open]] and [[Aneash Maglea]]'s private reception prior to the start of the [[Yacht/Legends|yacht]] race.

